innerComments.value: axios.post(URLDayl + "userLists/update", { id: paintId, listName: templistInfo.listName, detail: templistInfo.detail },
{/* <!-- SECTION PRESENTATION DE LA LISTE - début --> */}
{/* <!-- Modal modification de la liste - début --> */}
<input type="text" id="listName" size="35" value={templistInfo?.listName} onChange={e => setTempListInfo({ ...templistInfo, listName: e.target.value })} required />
<textarea id="listDesc" className="mb-b" maxlength="255" value={templistInfo?.detail} onChange={e => setTempListInfo({ ...templistInfo, detail: e.target.value })} />
<input type="submit" className="submit mt-b smart-modal-close" value="Enregistrer les modifications" style={{ position: "relative", right: "0", top: "0" }} />
{/* <!-- Modal modification de la liste - fin --> */}
